O prerender quebrava com 'Cannot read properties of null (useContext)':
clássico de DUAS cópias do React no monorepo — mobile (Expo 52) usa
react 18.3.1 e web (Next 15) usa react 19; o npm içava o 18 para a
raiz e as libs compartilhadas do painel (next-themes, react-query)
resolviam essa cópia, divergindo do react 19 do Next.

- raiz: react/react-dom ^19 em devDependencies — deps diretas da raiz
  têm prioridade de hoisting; o 18.3.1 aninha em apps/mobile (onde o
  Metro o resolve primeiro, comportamento correto para o Expo)
- web/tsconfig: isolatedModules true (o Next alterava no CI sem
  commitar; agora é reproduzível)
- apps/api/turbo.json: outputs [] (build é tsc --noEmit — remove o
  warning 'no output files found')

Após aplicar: npm install (re-hoisting) e commitar o package-lock.
---
 apps/api/turbo.json    |  8 ++++++++
 apps/web/tsconfig.json | 32 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++------
 package.json           |  4 +++-
 3 files changed, 37 insertions(+), 7 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 apps/api/turbo.json

diff --git a/apps/api/turbo.json b/apps/api/turbo.json
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..d7c7d48
--- /dev/null
+++ b/apps/api/turbo.json
@@ -0,0 +1,8 @@
+{
+  "extends": ["//"],
+  "tasks": {
+    "build": {
+      "outputs": []
+    }
+  }
+}
diff --git a/apps/web/tsconfig.json b/apps/web/tsconfig.json
index 60e78e4..4a24a36 100644
--- a/apps/web/tsconfig.json
+++ b/apps/web/tsconfig.json
@@ -1,14 +1,34 @@
 {
   "extends": "../../tsconfig.json",
   "compilerOptions": {
-    "lib": ["dom", "dom.iterable", "esnext"],
+    "lib": [
+      "dom",
+      "dom.iterable",
+      "esnext"
+    ],
     "jsx": "preserve",
     "noEmit": true,
     "allowJs": true,
     "incremental": true,
-    "plugins": [{ "name": "next" }],
-    "paths": { "@/*": ["./src/*"] }
+    "plugins": [
+      {
+        "name": "next"
+      }
+    ],
+    "paths": {
+      "@/*": [
+        "./src/*"
+      ]
+    },
+    "isolatedModules": true
   },
-  "include": ["next-env.d.ts", "**/*.ts", "**/*.tsx", ".next/types/**/*.ts"],
-  "exclude": ["node_modules"]
-}
+  "include": [
+    "next-env.d.ts",
+    "**/*.ts",
+    "**/*.tsx",
+    ".next/types/**/*.ts"
+  ],
+  "exclude": [
+    "node_modules"
+  ]
+}
\ No newline at end of file
diff --git a/package.json b/package.json
index a8a89f9..9dac730 100644
--- a/package.json
+++ b/package.json
@@ -26,7 +26,9 @@
     "turbo": "^2.3.3",
     "typescript": "^5.7.2",
     "prettier": "^3.4.2",
-    "@types/node": "^22.10.2"
+    "@types/node": "^22.10.2",
+    "react": "^19.0.0",
+    "react-dom": "^19.0.0"
   },
   "engines": {
     "node": ">=20.0.0",
